Insider Activity


Individual




Daniel R. Chard



Mr. Daniel R. Chard is on the Board of Directors at Medifast, Inc. Mr. Chard was previously employed as President & Chief Operating Officer by Partylite, Inc., Vice President-Marketing & Product Management by Big Planet, Inc., Senior Vice President-Marketing by Promedix.com, Inc., Senior Vice President-Marketing by Broadlane, Inc., President-Global Sales & Operations by Nu Skin Enterprises, Inc., and Senior Director-Marketing & Product Development by Pharmanex, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Brigham Young University and an MBA from the University of Minnesota.



